as the crystals\xa0provide a stable resonator which gives a constant electronic signal for the purpose of accurate timekeeping.\xa0

The watch comes with a plastic strap that increases the durability of this watch as the watch can be easily fastened or unfastened as you desire.\xa0The inclusion of a mineral glass\xa0cover provides great optical clarity and an added degree of damage-resistance to the dial.

This lovely Q&Q analog watch has been created for women who love a little hint of all things pretty and shiny in their look. The most appealing trait of this watch is that you can use it to dress up or dress down any outfit. You can easily pair this attractive watch with your party clothes. Just strap the watch with that black halter neck dress and put on the Q&Q watch and you are good to go.

    The analog watch also pairs perfectly well with your jeans and cute T-shirts giving you a well balanced outfit for a casual dinner date with friends. This trendy watch makes every woman look dashing and best of all it is a watch that doesn’t need you to change your wardrobe.

    The Q&Q watch sports a rectangular dial with designer patterns to add to its appeal. The small yet distinct time markers and the three hands help you tell time with ease. Elegant watches with excellent functionalities exemplify the Essentials collection from DKNY. Their stylish design is matched by the comfy features that these watches are equipped with.

Exemplifying great craftsmanship and eye-catching aesthetics is this exquisitely created women’s analog timepiece from the designer house of DKNY or Donna Karan New York

column17:
party and stand out in a crowd.

\r\n\tThe timekeeping function on this DKNY women\u2019s watch operates using the popular quartz crystal technology. This process works by generating an electrical charge which causes the crystals to vibrate thousand times a second
column18: making them extremely stable resonators for accurate timekeeping. In short
column19:
the battery-powered timepiece will never disappoint you with timekeeping.

Body and Design

\r\n\tThis highly stylized DKNY Essentials Analog Watch - For Women is built around a tonneau shaped dial that contains a watch face with a light-coloured background over which we find the two main watch hands that carry a bright and shiny metallic finish. Even the hour markers
column20:
which are depicted by small rectangular bars carry a similar metallic finish as the watch hands. This clever use of metallic elements against a light background not only adds to the style of the dial but also gives you clear and undisturbed reading of the dial.

\r\n\tThis thoughtfully conceived dial is enveloped by a very aesthetic stainless steel case that is designed to offer the dial considerable protection against impacts and shocks. Keeping this attractive dial comfortably attached to your wrist is the watch\u2019s extremely stylish two-toned stainless steel bracelet strap that operates like a jewellery clasp. The links on the strap are adjustable
column21: thus allowing you to change the length of the strap according to your convenience. The dial is capped with a highly durable and scratch-resistant mineral glass cover
column22:
which gives the dial the all-important sheen too.

Functions and Other Features

column25: this DKNY watch qualifies as your ideal companion for spending a lazy Sunday aside the club pool. Contemporary and exquisite

the DKNY Essentials analog watch is a perfect tribute to the modern woman who defines her existence through her poise.

The most appealing trait of this watch is that you can use it to dress up or dress down any outfit. You can easily pair this attractive watch with your party clothes. Just strap the watch with that black halter neck dress and put on the Q&Q watch and you are good to go.

    The analog watch also pairs perfectly well with your jeans and cute T-shirts giving you a well balanced outfit for a casual dinner date with friends. This trendy watch makes every woman look dashing and best of all it is a watch that doesn’t need you to change your wardrobe.

    Body and Design

    The Q&Q watch sports a rectangular dial with designer patterns to add to its appeal. The small yet distinct time markers and the three hands help you tell time with ease. This trendy watch for women is a product from the stables of Q&Q. The women’s watch is branded as a casual wear accessory that
column17: when the need presents itself
column18: can step up to being a party wear accessory as well. The analog Q&Q watch makes use of a battery powered quartz mechanism to keep the device ticking in perfect sync with your time zone. A quartz mechanism is a sure-fire
column19: as well as cost-effective
column20: way of knowing that you\u2019re timepiece will accurately adhere to international time keeping standards
column21:
no matter what.

Body and Design

To ensure the wearer with the utmost comfort while she sports the analog women’s Q&Q watch the designers of the elegant timepiece have equipped it with a soft leather strap. This leather strap is designed to fit snugly around the contours of your wrist for hours on end
column22:
while you work hard at office or carry out your daily chores at home.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe Q&Q watch for women is designed around a stainless steel case. This stainless steel case makes certain\xa0that the integral inner workings of the timepiece are not affected
column23: if and when the wristwatch is inadvertently dropped or otherwise mishandled. Moreover
column24:
it is this case that protects the intricately designed contemporary shaped dial.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe dial on the analog women\u2019s Q&Q watch
column25: with its three watch hands
column26: is accentuated by the ornamented bezel and bold index hour markers. These two features combine to make reading the time on the Q&Q watch very legible and even to some extent
column27:
delightful. This dial makes use of a mineral glass window to ensure that even the most determined of scratches do not find the their way on to the dial.

Functions and Other Features

The women’s analog watch from Q&Q is designed to be waterproof from minimal splashing. This water-resistant feature makes certain that timepiece keeps ticking
column28: even when your garden sprinkles switch on while you attempt to cover the distance between the sidewalk and main door. The women\u2019s Q&Q watch
column29: with its eloquent design and unmistakeable charm
column30:
proves to be the ideal accessory to adorn when you leave home.

column16:
'desc': [u'

Q&Q Analog Watch - For Women (Pink) Price: Rs.1255

Key Features

  • Pink Strap
  • Water Resistant

  • Rectangular Dial
  • Alloy Case
column17:
Metal Bezel \n

\r\n\tAs a glittering symbol of great craftsmanship and heightened aesthetics is this beautifully conceived timepiece from Q&Q\u2019s highly desirable line of women\u2019s analog watches. An ideal choice of personal timekeepers for the trendy and fashion conscious woman
column18: this analog watch from Q&Q accentuates in its wearer a sense of beauty and elegance
column19:
making it an automatic selection for all your casual events or parties.

Body and Design

The incredibly trendy women’s wristwatch from Q&Q features a fashionable rectangular dial that houses an attractive yet mellow background colour. This plain and solid coloured background features a metallic coloured design to disrupt the monotony of the watch face. The outermost track on the watch face carries the dial’s timekeeping markings in a dark colour; while the three watch hands carry a bright metallic colour. This clever use of different colours on the watch face
column20:
especially against such a light colour give you great dial visibility for easy time reading.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis highly creative and beautifully put together dial is surrounded by a thick alloy case that is designed to provide the dial with an improved level of durability and damage resistance. An alloy is a mixture that is composed of two or more metals
column21:
which in this case is aimed at producing a metal alloy that stronger and lighter than the original metal elements. This highly specialized alloy case while protecting the dial also contributes to the watch’s aesthetic value with its bright metallic finish which is encrusted with an array of stones or crystals.

The top and bottom portions of the bright metallic stone-studded alloy case have provision which allows the case to be attached to the watch’s classy and sensual leather strap that carries the same colour as the watch face. If you are someone who likes helping your mom out in their garden and don’t mind digging your hands into the dirt then the Q&Q watch is just right for you. The watch is protected with a mineral glass dial cover that keeps the watch safe from scratches. And even if you get a little dirt on the watch you can simply give it a thorough wash because the watch is water resistant up to a depth of 50 m. The plastic strap doesn’t get wet and can simply be wiped down to clean it.

Once you are done helping mom out you can head straight out to meet your friends at the beach. The snazzy sports watch is sure to match your ever so awesome swim wear so
column19: whether you choose to play volleyball on the beach or take a swim in sea
column20:
you look great with this dapper accessory. The Q&Q also features the very handy date display so you don’t have to fumble about with your phone to know what the date is.

This youthful watch from Q&Q is for the woman who is active and adventurous and needs a watch that can keep up with her busy and bustling life.

The splendour of a watch reflects the beauty of the lady wearing it. A watch that blends in seamlessly with your outfit for the day will surely boost your self confidence. Wear your style on your sleeves with this Esprit Analog Watch for women. Meant for wearing on any occasion
column15:
the timepiece is crafted specially for those women who love to flaunt their fine taste. The quartz timepiece oozes opulence from every inch and will not disappoint you when it comes to performance.

Body and Design

The dazzling Esprit analog women’s wristwatch makes for the perfect surprise gift for women on their birthdays or anniversaries. Classy appearance sets the watch apart from the assortment of other timekeeping devices. The round dial sports a shiny look
column16:
courtesy of the serene colours adorning it; the name of the company in the background accentuates the glamorous appeal.

\r\n

column17:

\r\n

\r\n\tThe stainless steel case enclosing the dial adds lustre to the time telling device. The sturdy metal alloy is resistant to corrosion and makes the prized time wear durable against the accidental damages. The dial also remains protected from accidental bumps and scratches
column18:
